Package: BEKKs
Title: Multivariate Conditional Volatility Modelling and Forecasting
Version: 1.4.5
Author: Markus J. Fülle [aut, cre], 
        Alexander Lange [aut],
        Christian M. Hafner [aut],
        Helmut Herwartz [aut]
